
'''Marie Béatrice Umutesi''' (wavutse 1959) ni umwanditsi w'[[Rwanda|umunyarwanda]] wandika mu [[Igifaransa|gifaransa]] . <ref name="uwa">http://aflit.arts.uwa.edu.au/UmutesiMBeng.html</ref>

Yavukiye i Byumba yiga sociology, akora mu iterambere ry'icyaro. Mbere ya [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|Genocide yakorewe abatuts]]<nowiki/>i mu [[Rwanda]] yafatwaga nk'umuntu ushyira mu gaciro,  yaje guhungira muri Kivu y'amajyaruguru muri [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo]], yahavuye muri 1996 ajya i [[Burayi]],  Umutesi yageze mu [[Ububiligi|Bubiligi]] muri 1998. '''<ref name="uwa" />'''<ref>https://books.google.com/books?id=X9pCh_N2atgC&pg=PA261</ref>

Yanditse inkuru yibyamubayeho muri ''Fuir ou mourir au Zaire.'' ''Le vécu d'une réfugiée Rwandaise'' (umutwe wicyongereza: ''Surviving the Slaughter:The Ordeal of a Rwandan Refugee in Zaire'' ). <ref>https://www.questia.com/library/journal/1G1-163049401/is-reconciliation-between-hutus-and-tutsis-possible</ref>

